One particularly wild material concept

Computational Fabric

A textile where each fiber is a tiny computing and sensing element.

Possible uses:
	•	clothing that monitors health
	•	tents that become communication hubs
	•	blankets that generate electricity
	•	uniforms that detect toxins

This would merge:

fabric
electronics
energy
AI sensing

into one material.

